The '''Shadow''' was a [[Muurian transport]] used by loyal [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces to install and activate [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] ''[[Vorknkx]]''{{'s}} [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]], as well as evacuate the research staff from platforms [[V1]] and [[V2]]. The research facility was under heavy assault by rogue [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Demetrius Zaarin]]'s traitorous forces, attempting to steal the new technology. The attack, however, was repelled by [[Tan (title)|Tan]] [[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]].

